ould in fact be used to constrain cosmological models, in cosmic microwave background maps but also in three-dimensional galaxy catalogues, where it estimates the total length of filaments in the Universe. Making the link with other works, we also show how the skeleton can be used to study the dynamics of large-scale structure. {\textcopyright} 2006 RAS.},
